profile: Aguiar Construction served the Greater Toronto Area for years before bringing the business to Northumberland, ON. Ronnie and his team bring over six years of experience in custom home building to their clients. We offer a variety of services and are always happy to connect with prospective clients to discuss new projects. Our top priority is bringing your vision of the perfect home to life, and we work closely with our clients throughout the building process to ensure satisfaction. Please do not hesitate to reach out for a free quote today.
